Introduction

YOUNGEST is a nine-member kids girl group under Kids Planet. They made their debut on September 7, 2016 with the release of their first digital single "Stand Up". They are the sister group of U.SSO Girl and Burvey.

Officially they have a generation system but it’s seems like members are always changing.
